	(651, '仓储金融服务', NULL, 0, 103, 104, '仓储金融科负责《仓储业务流程及操作规范》的制定和修改，并对实施情况进行监督。仓储金融科主管领导对仓储业务流程及操作规范进行总体控制，仓储金融科具体执行本办法。', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="NewNewNewNewNew" style="line-height:200%">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">目的：</span></b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; ">规范仓储业务流程及操作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体">适用范围：</span></b><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">本办法适用于</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">仓储</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">业务</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">的管理与操作。<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">职责：</span></b><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">仓储金融科</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">负责《</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">仓储</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">业务流程及操作规范》的制定和修改，并对实施情况进行监督。</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">仓储金融</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">科主管领导对</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">仓储</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">业务流程及操作规范进行总体控制，</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">仓储金融</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; ">科具体执行本办法。</span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: 宋体; "><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="NewNewNewNewNew" style="line-height:200%">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; ">一、仓储业务<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="NewNewNewNewNew" style="line-height:200%">\r\n	<b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-heigh